"data/events_sector_aea_shard.xml$//event[@name=\"AEA_SHARD_PALACE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“你能不受阻拦地来到这里，这令人担忧。不过，你或许来得正是时候。你可能已经看到"
"了我们外面的问题，一个更强大的碎晶铸者氏族前来挑战我的统治，他们想夺取黎明碎"
"片，控制碎晶铸者。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_aea_shard.xml:1108
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_aea_shard.xml$//event[@name=\"AEA_SHARD_PALACE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_aea_shard.xml:1110
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_aea_shard.xml$//event[@name=\"AEA_SHARD_PALACE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“这意味着他们必须杀死我，从我尸体上取走它。你愿意帮我潜入你的星舰吗？我可以加"
"入你的船员，让我的将军们来处理这个局面？如果夺取黎明碎片已不可能，上面那些氏"
"族的成员就不太愿意发动战争了。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_aea_shard.xml:1112
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_aea_shard.xml$//event[@name=\"AEA_SHARD_PALACE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "接纳他上船。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_aea_shard.xml:1114
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_aea_shard.xml$//event[@name=\"AEA_SHARD_PALACE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“太好了，我离开时就藏在这件大外套里，希望上面的星舰不会来找我们的麻烦。”你向"
"外走，回到你的星舰。你成功登上了自己的星舰，看起来上面的星舰都没有注意到。但"
"就在你起飞时，旁边一艘大型星舰移动过来挡住了你的路。它似乎在干扰你的超光速驱"
"动器，阻止你离开。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_aea_shard.xml:1116
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_aea_shard.xml$//event[@name=\"AEA_SHARD_PALACE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/crewMember"
